If you are bored with successful build.
If you want to taste the pleasure of a smart crash.
Then the maven-fail-plugin is made for you.

The incomparable experience will be served by the amazing features : 
customization : 
 - message of thrown exception.
 - phase of failure.
reliability : 
 - 100% guaranted satisfation
lightness : 
 - 3k jar 
 - no dependancy !

